'''Fastmail'''（旧版写作'''FastMail'''）一项由[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]公司 Fastmail Pty Ltd 提供的[[电子邮件|电子邮件]]服务，因最早提供免费[[IMAP|IMAP]]邮件服务而出名。2010年，該公司被[[Opera_Software|Opera]]收購。2013年9月26日，Fastmail宣布從Opera分離，成為一家私人控股的獨立公司<ref>{{cite news |url=http://ceoworld.biz/ceo/2013/09/26/australian-based-email-provider-fastmail-became-a-privately-held-independent-company-29920932 |title=FastMail became a privately held independent company |publisher=CEOWORLD Magazine |accessdate=2013-09-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928014101/http://ceoworld.biz/ceo/2013/09/26/australian-based-email-provider-fastmail-became-a-privately-held-independent-company-29920932 |archivedate=2013-09-28 }}</ref>。至今Fastmail在国際上仍是最受欢迎的[[IMAP|IMAP]]邮件服务之一，而在中国则受到[[Gmail|Gmail]]对[[IMAP|IMAP]]的支持的冲击。Fastmail拥有数十个提供服务的域名。

在一項非正式的評比中，Fastmail的安全性與[[Gmail|Gmail]]並列A級第二，A級第一是[https://Mail.de Mail.de]{{Wayback|url=https://mail.de/ |date=20200901024215 }}。A級的條件：除了User - Server間的傳輸用TLS 1.2加密之外，Server - Server的送信、收信也必須支援TLS 1.2加密，才能保證傳輸的任何一段過程皆不被偷窺。世界各國Email服務中能達到頂尖的不到5家。但Fastmail由於伺服器設在侵犯網路隱私惡名昭彰的美國（關鍵字：[[稜鏡計畫|稜鏡計畫]]），因此雖有技術上的安全性，仍不能保證美國政府不透過施壓業者的方式、不需竊聽即可取得通訊內容；所以Fastmail和Gmail在這項評比中被列為第二。<ref>{{cite web|title=Email大小事：安全性、加密技術、服務業者的選擇|url=http://rechtsgut.pixnet.net/blog/post/31156447-email%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B%EF%BC%9A%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E3%80%81%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E6%A5%AD%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84|accessdate=2013-09-20|date=2013-09-09|work=披星戴月 後知後覺|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031114759/http://rechtsgut.pixnet.net/blog/post/31156447-email%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B%EF%BC%9A%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E3%80%81%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E6%A5%AD%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84|archivedate=2013-10-31|deadurl=yes}}</ref>{{Better source|reason=此段描述的“评比”来自2013年的一篇个人博客。建议替换为近期权威机构的评比。|date=2021年7月}}

==历史==

Fastmail 于 1999 年由 Rob Mueller, Bruce Davey 和 Jeremy Howard 创建。

2010 年被 Opera 收购。2013 年重新成为独立公司。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2010/04/30/fastmail_fm_opera/|title=Opera targets mobile with email acquisition|work=[[The_Register|The Register]]|accessdate=16 September 2010|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810170459/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2010/04/30/fastmail_fm_opera/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.arnnet.com.au/article/345171/opera_software_purchases_melbourne-based_email_provider/?fp=4&fpid=56736|title=Opera Software purchases Melbourne-based email provider|website=Arnnet.com.au|accessdate=16 September 2010|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810210248/https://www.arnnet.com.au/article/345171/opera_software_purchases_melbourne-based_email_provider/?fp=4&fpid=56736|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.opera.com/press/releases/2010/04/30/ |title=Opera acquires Fastmail.fm |website=Opera.com |date=2010-04-30 |accessdate=2016-12-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66XFSb8PF?url=http://www.opera.com/press/releases/2010/04/30/ |archive-date=2012-03-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="FMB">{{cite web|title=FastMail.FM has been acquired by Opera Software|url=http://blog.fastmail.com/2010/04/30/fastmail-fm-has-been-acquired-by-opera-software/|website=Blog.fastmail.com|accessdate=21 August 2010|archive-date=2014-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141227202249/http://blog.fastmail.com/2010/04/30/fastmail-fm-has-been-acquired-by-opera-software/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref><!-- Yes, corporate blogs can be considered reliable sources.--> {{cite web|title=Exciting news: FastMail staff purchase the business from Opera|url=https://blog.fastmail.com/2013/09/25/exciting-news-fastmail-staff-purchase-the-business-from-opera/|website=Blog.fastmail.com|accessdate=18 July 2016|archive-date=2017-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706171951/https://blog.fastmail.com/2013/09/25/exciting-news-fastmail-staff-purchase-the-business-from-opera/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012-10-18 起，Fastmail 不再接受新的免费用户注册。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.fastmail.com/2012/10/18/changes-to-fastmail-service-levels/|title=Changes to FastMail service levels|website=Blog.fastmail.com|accessdate=2016-12-06|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020141056/https://blog.fastmail.com/2012/10/18/changes-to-fastmail-service-levels/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 现有的免费用户可继续使用，但若免费账户 120 天未登录，即会被删除。Fastmail 公司认为此举有助于他们为付费用户提供更优质的服务。

2014-10-23 起，Fastmail 的主域名由 <code>fastmail.fm</code> 改为 <code>fastmail.com</code>。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.fastmail.com/2014/10/23/fastmail-has-moved-to-fastmail-com-fastmail-com-email-addresses-now-available/|title=FastMail has moved to fastmail.com, @fastmail.com email addresses now available|website=Blog.fastmail.com|accessdate=2016-12-06|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220235810/https://blog.fastmail.com/2014/10/23/fastmail-has-moved-to-fastmail-com-fastmail-com-email-addresses-now-available/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019-06-24 起，Fastmail 采用新的网站设计，其品牌的拼写由 '''FastMail''' 改为 '''Fastmail'''。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://fastmail.blog/2019/06/24/fastmail-new-logo/|title=A new look, logo, and website for Fastmail|website=Fastmail Blog|access-date=2019-06-25|archive-date=2019-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190625012731/https://fastmail.blog/2019/06/24/fastmail-new-logo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

